[32m+[m[32m## Additional Utilities[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### EMBER Utilities (`ember_utils.py`)[m
[32m+[m[32mStandalone functions for accessing EMBER electricity generation data:[m
[32m+[m[32m- `get_total_electricity_generation(iso_code, year)` - Get total generation in TWh[m
[32m+[m[32m- `get_generation_by_fuel(iso_code, year)` - Get fuel breakdown by type[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### 8760 Supply Constructor (`scripts/8760_supply_demand_constructor.py`)[m
[32m+[m[32mComplete system for building 8760-hour supply and demand profiles:[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Baseline generation**: Nuclear (flat) + Hydro (demand-shaped) from EMBER data[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Renewable integration**: Solar and wind from REZoning with hourly shapes[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Visualization**: Quarterly charts and supply curve analysis[m
[32m+[m
